a":{"origin":37131,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: Entire earth place of prayer except graveyards, bathrooms","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe entire earth has been made a place of prayer,\u00a0except for graveyards and washrooms.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 317 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Taymiyyah \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37133,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/14\/haram-build-sit-salat-graves\/","url_meta":{"origin":37131,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Qubur: Forbidden to build, sit, or pray over graves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa'id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited building over graves, sitting upon them, or praying over them. Source: Musnad Abi\u0304 Ya\u2019la\u0301 1020 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\