, \u201cIndeed, I said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39736,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/17\/angels-speak-tongues\/","url_meta":{"origin":37131,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Angels: Truth spoken by angels on tongues of people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 17, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has angels who speak upon the tongues of the children of Adam about whether a man was good or evil.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 9318 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2903,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/16\/la-qabr-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":37131,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Graves: Do not turn homes into graves, or graves into celebrations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not turn your houses into graves, and do not turn my grave into a place of festivity. Send blessings upon me, for your blessings will reach me wherever you are.\" Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2042\u2026","rel":"","context":"